{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-excerpt-js","path":"/excerpts/burn_cities/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Burn all the cities and plant trees,<br>\nSmash the melting pot of disease,<br>\nRoots and leaves over walls and beams,<br>\nAir that doesn't kill you to breath,<br>\nWealth and poverty's dirty orgy,<br>\nWith rent boy and hooker herpes,<br>\nSwarming with blight and mindless yobs,<br>\nWorking class work underpaid jobs,<br>\nColour's better than shades of grey,<br>\nThe earth as she is meant to be,<br>\nStand by flora not on hardcore,<br>\nHear the songs of birds not harsh words,<br>\nWould they notice smog change to smoke,<br>\nWould we care as they start to choke,<br>\nWe'd mourn for a day for our loss,<br>\nCleansed of their stone metropolis.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 03, 2020","title":"Burn Cities","audio":{"publicURL":"/static/a9f124e89fc7bea500fb389c8ce51267/burn_cities.mp3"},"icon":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/521716c9002ce8b28e4ee91b60d42fea/ee604/burn_cities.png","srcSet":"/static/521716c9002ce8b28e4ee91b60d42fea/69585/burn_cities.png 200w,\n/static/521716c9002ce8b28e4ee91b60d42fea/497c6/burn_cities.png 400w,\n/static/521716c9002ce8b28e4ee91b60d42fea/ee604/burn_cities.png 800w,\n/static/521716c9002ce8b28e4ee91b60d42fea/f3583/burn_cities.png 1200w,\n/static/521716c9002ce8b28e4ee91b60d42fea/5707d/burn_cities.png 1600w,\n/static/521716c9002ce8b28e4ee91b60d42fea/ed396/burn_cities.png 2000w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/excerpts/burn_cities/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}